{"tid":2248780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：美國手伸得好長 但我每次都會對美國作出強烈譴責和反駁","createTime":"2020-10-19T00:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T07:05:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":26,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"b104b2086bfafd455c16b14245d00db188823e90","tid":2248780,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:43:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥表示「跨境理財通」的額度和「先行先試」的產品仍在與內地磋商中，表明框架既然已經出台便不會「走數」，形容措施即將來臨，不用等施政報告。 <br />\n<br />\n香港牽涉中美角力當中，林鄭月娥指，現階段沒措施可協助金融機構抵禦政治風險，形容美方手伸得好長，但政府每次都會對美國作出強烈譴責和反駁。林鄭月娥又指，香港現時「有危有機」，美國打壓中資企業，衍生中概股回流在港第二上市的機遇，期望繼阿里巴巴等企業後，餘下3個月會再有多些股份回流。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362184&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=3b2a3a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362184</a>"},{"pid":"2a03f1544d3f303bf1ca06b92ce834910f82038c","tid":2248780,"uid":41873,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:44:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我每次都會對美國打嘴炮 滿足藍絲弱小心靈</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cbe60d220ed4f76c1d9d81cf328c949528b40408","tid":2248780,"uid":41873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:44:52.000Z","msg":"推返先sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24a09865250f5f9ea030a884b394b3563fad599","tid":2248780,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:45:07.000Z","msg":"罰自已推多兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bc5394fd2f741f5aed083c9d6fd594a6a44f6c","tid":2248780,"uid":41873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"推埋呢下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sow