<span class=\"red\">她又提到，應對造地問題感到辛苦，政治氣氛和保育意識高漲，有一班人與政府對抗拖慢進度，土地開發較97年時艱難十倍</span>，政府現時把球場和運動場等改成「插針樓」，只是「短暫止痛藥」，認為倒不如改善收地賠償和安置等，爭取一次過開拓一、兩千公頃土地。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，正研究加快推進與深圳和大灣區的創科協同發展，包括與深圳商議推出「聯合政策包」，吸引在美國的內地企業到香港上市和在美華人到香港或者深圳發展。林鄭月娥又提到，希望吸引著名海外學者來港，正在構思政策，希望稍後可以公布。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362184&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=3b2a3a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362184</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:07:27.000Z","msg":"咪唔好造囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有機會逼走班新腥港人仲好添"},{"pid":"a9da9571fbec43644026ff759d8cb5bbc402101b","tid":2248780,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:15:34.000Z","msg":"*************<br />\n強烈反對美國<br />\n完<br />\n*************"},{"pid":"d133d8e9f749236173b393c707c59298fa6a6eed","tid":2248780,"uid":260251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2236cb567a9d6451fa36f00e30503f3b15f874b6","tid":2248780,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"香港最勁嘅武器除左水炮車就係嘴炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e21f5670bfaa29a362d8e0c6ff0b5ecc0ecf3a0","tid":2248780,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f365ee864489e51cc6996a6a122900708b4ff348","tid":2248780,"uid":59863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a5f2f749fa367d38523e95ca0b6515358f6c520","tid":2248780,"uid":211466,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"2a03f1544d3f303bf1c